                    <h3 class="gh-list-item-title">Kale Salad with Honey’d Walnuts</h3>
                <p class="gh-list-item-excerpt text-action text-brown-40 before:hidden">Kale salad, how 2013, I know. But it’s undeniably a great candidate for a meal like this. It’s sturdy, almost masquerading as a side instead of a salad, it’s one of the only salad greens that get better with age and can even be saved as a leftover with little to no consequences.</p>
